           <h3 style="color: #CC0000">MAYFAIR DARJELLING</h3>
           &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
                 Located in the lap of Mother Nature, is a star category deluxe heritage hotel that was once the summerhouse of Maharaja of Nazargunj. Located at prime location (opposite Governor's House) in Darjeeling, MAYFAIR Darjeeling is known for world-class facilities, state-of-the-art services, superb amenities, and a home like surrounding that pleases ever tourist. With 43 well-decorated and fully furnished rooms,the leading luxury hotel in Darjeeling provide you accommodation with the motive of "Stay with Us, Stay with Nature". Being over a century old, it still maintains the charm of the old world while having modern amenities and a young and vibrant staff. Warm fires in each room, spectacular sunsets, the stellar Spa, an exclusive Tea boutique and extensive dining options are just some of the reasons guests come back here time and again.
                 <br />
                 <br />
        <h3 style="color: #CC0000">THE ROYAL HERITAGE</h3>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Set in Gangtok, 1.6 km from Palzor Stadium, The Royal Heritage offers accommodation with a restaurant, free private parking and a bar. A hot tub and a bicycle rental service are available for guests. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi.
All guest rooms at the hotel come with a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels and a private bathroom with free toiletries and a shower. Guest rooms will provide guests with a desk and a kettle.
The Royal Heritage offers a continental or buffet breakfast.Enchey Monastery is 2.6 km from the accommodation, while Do Drul Chorten Monastery is 3.1 km from the property.
                 <br />
                 <br />
                 <h3 style="color: #CC0000">MAGELLAN'S THE GRAND LACHEN</h3>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
The Grand Lachen is located at Lachen, North Sikkim an ideal stay on the way to Gurudongmar Lake. You can enjoy the enchanting views of Mt. Kangchendzonga from Rooms and Terrace. This hotel is well-suited for families holiday travellers Lachen is a village in North Sikkim, at an altitude of 8500ft. Lachen is alluring in its simplicity. The name Lachen means “big pass”, forms the base to the Chopta Valley and Gurudongmar Lake. Lachen is about 129 kms from Gangtok and can be reached via a six-hour road journey. Gurudongmar Lake can be reached from Lachen, a sacred lake in the Great Himalayas Region.


                 <br />
                 <br />
                 <h3 style="color: #CC0000">DELIGHT ROYAL LACHUNG</h3>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Delight Royal Lachung is a pure veg hotel with ostentatious and extravagant to the very core. Majestic facade, elegant interiors, opulent furnishings and an ultimate service, all make the hotel a favourite with visitors to the valley. With its well decorated rooms, the hotel has a lot to offer to its guests. Each room comes fitted with the best of amenities and facilities.


                 <br />
                 <br />
                 <h3 style="color: #CC0000">SUMMIT GOLDEN CRESCENT</h3>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Experience a new level of sophistication at Summit Golden Crescent & Spa. Located close to the heart of the city, the hotel offers all the services which are ideal for couples, families, groups and business travelers. The hotel's point of difference is its emphasis on appealing designs, a warm and welcoming environment with careful attention to details and personalized service. The decor' is a celebration of contemporary art and design with hints of the warm Sikkimese hospitality. The multi-purpose hall, kid's zone and spa make this hotel a unique place to be. Also the lawn inside this golden property is a place to relax, perhaps with a book and a cappuccino from our Cafe. Refreshments are served throughout the day and evening cocktails are the time to enjoy a private drink with your partner or to meet other guests and discuss the day's adventures at The Bar. Summit Golden is known for privacy, discretion, luxury and serenity.
